  ``!g:'a monoid. Monoid g ==> !x y. x IN G /\ y IN G /\ (x * y = y * x) ==> !n. (x * y) ** n = (x ** n) * (y ** n)``,
  rpt strip_tac >>
  Induct_on `n` >-
  rw[] >>
  `(x * y) ** SUC n = x * ((y * (x ** n)) * (y ** n))` by rw[monoid_assoc] >>
  `_ = x * (((x ** n) * y) * (y ** n))` by metis_tac[monoid_comm_exp] >>
  rw[monoid_assoc]);

